{"tid":674984,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS5 或將採用 AMD Ryzen 處理器","createTime":"2018-05-23T07:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T10:15:59.000Z","uid":1886,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bfd6c087a99b1eec21f3cc1a44caacdb5f783b9b","tid":674984,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:13:31.000Z","msg":"雖然 Sony 已經表明今年的 E3 2018 電玩娛樂展，並不會公佈全新的 PlayStation 5 遊戲主機，而之前亦有指新主機要到 2019 或 2020 年才會發表，不過有關新主機的消息日前還是傳出，有外國傳媒發現 Sony 的工程師正在針對 AMD Ryzen 處理器進行研發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，相信是為 PS5 作準備。<br />\n<br />\n報導指 Sony 的高級工程師 Simon Pilgrim 正在研究如何使用 LLVM 編譯器，以達到完善 AMD Ryzen 處理器效能，因為 Pilgrim 在 PS3 和 PS4 主機都是開發團隊的主力，所以外國媒體認為，Sony 正在為下一代遊戲主機 PS5 的硬件進行準備。報導有太多 Pilgrim 目前正埋首於 znver1 架構，它正是初代 Ryzen 處理器，不過 PS5 會否採用更新的 Ryzen 處理器現在則未有答案。<br />\n<br />\n由於現時 PS4 採用的 Jaguar 架構處理器已經無法滿足遊戲的需求，所以有傳聞 Sony 會在 PS5 選用 AMD Ryzen 處理器。至於對遊戲機相當重要的圖像處理器，有指 Sony 將會在 Vega 和 Navi 兩者中作出選擇，有消息指 Sony 會選擇基於 7nm 製程的 AMD 圖像處理器。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/05/21/sony-ps5-amd-ryzen/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2Fsony-ps5-amd-ryzen%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=iJ1hh9eUCMnYa1jZs1pE9ghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=11520c1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/05/21/sony-ps5-amd-ryzen/game-channel/</a>"},{"pid":"43cb62d7d19c6cedadd13a49a4dd099b360faa95","tid":674984,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:15:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=60030&amp;page=&amp;snA=494031&amp;last=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D60030%26page%3D%26snA%3D494031%26last%3D&d=iJ1hh9eUCMnYa1jZs1pE9ghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=7ea90011\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=60030&amp;page=&amp;snA=494031&amp;last=</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201805/b955e0d0b8f9fb44e5f3dd5b6b3e4e66.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201805%2Fb955e0d0b8f9fb44e5f3dd5b6b3e4e66.JPG&h=c0a1fbac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPlayStation 5 將採用8核心ZEN + NAVI GPU<br />\n<br />\n估計效能約在1800X + Vega 56<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201805/1a6fe8371c6ae9ae3d8761d503a75268.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201805%2F1a6fe8371c6ae9ae3d8761d503a75268.JPG&h=b5313bf8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07100f1105c874668bc0b731231955658a8c9fb0","tid":674984,"uid":8659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:18:40.000Z","msg":"有1800X咁上下都算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a19934076911018fac76f8c19cb1a1e43b1908e5","tid":674984,"uid":50124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:35:01.000Z","msg":"仲&quot;或&quot;乜鬼,有得唔用Ryzen咩"},{"pid":"0e0f15412b79149da5ac4097049d00c0be60725f","tid":674984,"uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a19934076911018fac76f8c19cb1a1e43b1908e5","tid":674984,"uid":50124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:35:01.000Z","msg":"仲&quot;或&quot;乜鬼,有得唔用Ryzen咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T09:28:52.000Z","msg":"Sony要慳錢既話用粒手機級CPU都得，齋upgrade GPU出PS5"},{"pid":"326412e3a978bb95653f47ef171a5b9f5d55bf02","tid":674984,"uid":50124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e0f15412b79149da5ac4097049d00c0be60725f","tid":674984,"uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a19934076911018fac76f8c19cb1a1e43b1908e5","tid":674984,"uid":50124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:35:01.000Z","msg":"仲&quot;或&quot;乜鬼,有得唔用Ryzen咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T09:28:52.000Z","msg":"Sony要